snippet.title: sm64coopdx Official Trailer
snippet.description:
At last! Here is a video after a month of about non stop working.

sm64coopdx is a project started by the Coop Deluxe team to actively maintain as a fork, improve on and provide a better community for sm64ex-coop. We are adding more features, customizability, and power to the Lua API without having to jump through the many hoops of issues sm64ex-coop development has, or deal with cool new features being turned down by overly cautious developers.

Trailer by @angelicmiracles
sm64coopdx by Coop Deluxe Team
Gun Mod DX By Agent X
Day Night Cycle DX By Agent X
Arena w/ Rainbow Road By @angelicmiracles
Character Select by @Squishy6094

The download is at https://sm64coopdx.com
